  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:22:33.384180+00:00",
  "text": "when I set empty string to include in keepalive , I hope it will never cache any component.But now,it is a bit counter-intuitive\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.4\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. click button to switch component and input something\r\n2. After that, toggle,and component  still be cached\n\n### What is expected?\n\nno cache anything\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\ncache as not set it\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
